ory\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/fudayl-ignorant-sultan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36590,"position":2},"title":"Fudayl on Sultan: Ignorant rulers ascend when believers disobey Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn al-Ash\u2019ath reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty revealed to some of His Prophets: When those who know Me disobey Me, I will make them be ruled by those who do not know Me.\u201d Source: al-'Uqu\u0304ba\u0304t li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 33 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20449,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/08\/ahnaf-on-hasad-no-rest\/","url_meta":{"origin":36590,"position":3},"title":"Ahnaf on Envy: No rest for the envious, hateful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 8, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bayhaqi reported: Al-Ahnaf ibn Qays, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cFive are as I say: There is no rest for the envious, there is no manhood for the liar, there is no loyalty for kings, there is no escape for the miser, and there is no respect for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43851,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/07\/03\/ahmad-cursing-makruh\/","url_meta":{"origin":36590,"position":4},"title":"Ahmad on Curses: Disapproval of praying against people by name","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Salih reported: A man mentioned Al-Hajjaj or others to his father, Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah be pleased with him, saying, \u201cLet him be cursed!\u201d Ahmad said, \u201cI do not like for it to be uttered.\u201d Then, Ahmad said, \u201cSurely, the curse of Allah is upon the wrongdoers.\u201d (11:18) Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38854,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/21\/companions-muslim-rulers\/","url_meta":{"origin":36590,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Companions forbid supplicating against Muslim rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The eminent among the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us, saying, \u201cDo not curse your leaders, do not deceive them, and do not hate them. Fear Allah and be patient, for the matter is close at hand.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36590","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[